title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Pick 3” game were:
4-9-0
(four, nine, zero)
